                    eng: "Interesting things starts when we put both portals in one world.

This scene showed two portals against in front of each other. Triangle always moves forward, but portals teleport it, so movement cycled.

Notice that when we look at blue portal, we see only this blue portal; similarly with the orange portal; and when look at triangle we always see its back.

